# =============================================================================
# APPLICATION SPECIFIC
# =============================================================================
.storage/
repomix-output*
# The bundled SQLite index (data/medical-codes.db) is a deterministic build
# artifact (>100 MB), kept out of git but shipped in the npm tarball (.npmignore
# does not exclude it) and the Docker image. Obtain it from the GitHub Release
# assets or rebuild it with scripts/build-index.ts. Everything under data/
# (scratch DBs, source extracts) is ignored too.
data/
# Federal source files the build script ingests (extracted ZIPs / order files /
# tabular XML). The build input, re-downloadable from the .gov URLs — never
# committed.
.sources/
# Generated test fixture DB (built on demand by tests/helpers/index-fixture.ts).
tests/fixtures/*.db
docs/api/
docs/devdocs.md
.mcp.json
.claude/
.agents/
.mcpregistry_github_token
.mcpregistry_registry_token

# Internal design brief (catalog frontmatter) — local only, not for public repo
docs/idea.md
